    <item>
      <title>First post</title>
      <link>/en/post/my-first-post/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/en/post/my-first-post/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This website was created in order to keep track of my academic progress, and with the intention of posting about matters that I may find interesting. The perspectives here shown are not necessarily associated with the 
&lt;a href=&#34;http://complex.pfi.uem.br&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;ComplexLab&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fun fact: this website, ansesu, is name after the initials of &lt;strong&gt;An&lt;/strong&gt;dré &lt;strong&gt;Se&lt;/strong&gt;iji &lt;strong&gt;Su&lt;/strong&gt;nahara, since its abbreviation may sound a little rude.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The photo shown below pictures me and my 
&lt;a href=&#34;http://complex.pfi.uem.br&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;ComplexLab&lt;/a&gt; friends at the time of my dissertation defense.&lt;/p&gt;





  
  











